public abstract class MetaMetadataLinksetParser
extends MetaMetadataParserBase
implements ecologylab.generic.DispatchTarget<Container>

This is the base class for all seeds which bascially return a collection of links to be interleaved with other seeds. Example of such seeds are search result pages and feeds.
